Method Summary

  • ~ (void) nextTime() Used to generate timestamps for visualization test data.
  • ~ (void) window.nextTimeEntry() Used to generate entries for test visualization
  • ~ (void) hist_nextTime() Independent timestamp generation method for heatmap test data
  • ~ (void) window.nextHistEntry(hist_range = [0, 100], time) Generates an entry containing a histogram for heatmap test data
  • ~ (void) window.nextHeatmapEntry() Generates a fullly layered entry for heatmap test data
  • ~ (void) window.nextMultiLayerHeatmapEntry() Generates entries for multi-layered heatmap data with varying distributions
